# Plesk Deployment Configuration

## Node.js App Settings
Startup File: server.js
Node Version: 18.x or higher
App Mode: Production

## Build Command
npm run build

## Start Command
npm start

## Environment Variables
NODE_ENV=production
NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=https://yourdomain.com
PORT=3000

## Required Files
- server.js (custom server)
- package.json
- next.config.mjs
- .next/ (generated after build)
- public/
- app/
- components/
- lib/

